@host = http://localhost:8000
@token = {{$dotenv DRF_TOKEN}}

### List connected accounts
GET {{host}}/api/v1/accounts/
Authorization: Token {{token}}

### Get Instagram OAuth URL (open the returned url in a browser)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/accounts/instagram/connect/
Authorization: Token {{token}}

### Get Threads OAuth URL
GET {{host}}/api/v1/accounts/threads/connect/
Authorization: Token {{token}}

### Connect WhatsApp (paste WABA credentials from Meta Business Manager)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/accounts/whatsapp/
Authorization: Token {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone_number_id": "REPLACE_PHONE_NUMBER_ID",
  "access_token": "REPLACE_PERMANENT_SYSTEM_USER_TOKEN"
}

### Link knowledge to an account / toggle auto-reply
PATCH {{host}}/api/v1/accounts/REPLACE_ACCOUNT_ID/
Authorization: Token {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "knowledge_id": "REPLACE_KNOWLEDGE_ID",
  "auto_reply_enabled": true
}

### Disconnect
DELETE {{host}}/api/v1/accounts/REPLACE_ACCOUNT_ID/
Authorization: Token {{token}}

### Reply logs (filter: ?account=<id>&status=sent|failed|skipped)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/replies/?limit=20
Authorization: Token {{token}}
